RTCCodecStatsClockRate.summary: The clockRate property of the dictionary is a positive number containing the media sampling rate in hertz (Hz).

remarks.para:
-codecs.clockRate option in parameter passed to RTCRtpTransceiver.setCodecPreferences() and RTCRtpSender.setParameters().
-codecs.clockRate in object returned by RTCRtpSender.getParameters() and RTCRtpReceiver.getParameters().

RTCCodecStatsClockRate.value: A positive number indicating the media sampling rate.
